---
const { title } = Astro.props;
const pathName = Astro.url.pathname;
const gitBookUrl = "https://skolomorphic.github.io" + pathName + '#comments';
---
<section id="comments">
    <h1 class="comment-header">Comments</h1>
    <div class="notice">
        <p>Hi! If you'd like to share your thoughts or ask a question, you can email me at 
            <a>skolomorphic@protonmail.com</a>, visit me on <a href="http://skolomorphic.tumblr.com/">tumblr</a>, 
            or leave a comment below.</p>
        <p>Please note that <strong>likes & comments do not work on the neocities mirror of my website</strong>
        due to content restriction policies. If you are visiting this page from neocities, you can comment on
        the <a href={gitBookUrl}>Github Books</a> page instead.</p>
        <p>I look forward to hearing from you.</p>
        <p>Thanks for visiting my page!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="commentbox-wrapper">  
        <!-- customize labels of htmlcommentbox.com -->
        <script is:inline data-astro-rerun type="text/javascript" define:vars={{pathName}}>
            /* This code goes ABOVE the main HTML Comment Box code!
            replace the text in the single quotes below to customize labels.*/
            hcb_user = {
                /* L10N */
                comments_header : 'Page Comments',
                logout_link : '<img title="log out" src="https://www.htmlcommentbox.com/static/images/door_out.svg" alt="[logout]" class="hcb-icon hcb-door-out"/>',
                admin_link : '<img src="https://www.htmlcommentbox.com/static/images/door_in.svg" alt="[login]" class="hcb-icon hcb-door-in"/>',
                rss:'<i class="fas fa-rss"></i> Subscribe to this comment feed',
                prev_page:'<img src="https://www.htmlcommentbox.com/static/images/arrow_left.png" class="hcb-icon" title="previous page" alt="[prev]"/>',
                next_page:'<img src="https://www.htmlcommentbox.com/static/images/arrow_right.png" class="hcb-icon" title="next page" alt="[next]"/>',
                PAGE: `${pathName}` /* ID of the webpage to show comments for. defaults to the webpage the user is currently visiting. */
            };
        </script>
        <!-- done customizing labels of htmlcommentbox.com -->
        <!-- begin wwww.htmlcommentbox.com -->
        <div id="HCB_comment_box"><a href="http://www.htmlcommentbox.com">Comment Box</a> is loading comments...</div>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://www.htmlcommentbox.com/static/skins/bootstrap/twitter-bootstrap.css?v=0" />
        <script is:inline data-astro-rerun type="text/javascript" id="hcb"> /*<!--*/ if(!window.hcb_user){hcb_user={}; console.log('hcb user?!', hcb_user);} (function(){var s=document.createElement("script"), l=hcb_user.PAGE || (""+window.location).replace(/'/g,"%27"), h="https://www.htmlcommentbox.com";s.setAttribute("type","text/javascript");s.setAttribute("src", h+"/jread?page="+encodeURIComponent(l).replace("+","%2B")+"&mod=%241%24wq1rdBcg%24xlen81zX4BBvw6b8mSiAp%2F"+"&opts=16798&num=10&ts=1742707546107");if (typeof s!="undefined") document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0].appendChild(s);})(); /*-->*/ </script>
        <!-- end www.htmlcommentbox.com -->
        <p id="commentcredit">Comments powered by <a href="https://www.htmlcommentbox.com/"><strong>HTML Comment Box</strong></a>.</p>
    </div>
</section>
<style is:global>     
#comments {
    margin-top: 50px;
}
.comment-header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-light);
}
.notice {
    padding: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: 'Source Code Pro', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background-color: var(--accent-ultralight);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.notice p {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.notice p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
}
.commentbox-wrapper {
    padding: 5px 15px;
    background-color: var(--accent-ultralight);
    border-radius: 5px;
}

/* html comment box */
#HCB_comment_box h3 {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-dark);
}
#HCB_comment_box .comment {
    padding-left: 16px;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--accent-dark);
}
#HCB_comment_box #hcb_msg {
    margin: 5px auto;
}
#HCB_comment_box .hcb-comment-tb button {
    color: var(--accent-contrast-light) !important;
}
#HCB_comment_box #hcb_submit {
    background-color:var(--accent-midtone) !important;
    border:1px solid var(--accent-midtone) !important;
    color: var(--body-font);
}

#HCB_comment_box #hcb_form_content,
  #HCB_comment_box #hcb_form_email,
  #HCB_comment_box #hcb_form_name,
  #HCB_comment_box #hcb_form_website {
    background-color: var(--accent-light);
    color: var(--body-font);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-midtone);
  }
  #HCB_comment_box .home-desc {
    display: none;
  }
#HCB_comment_box a {
    color: var(--accent-contrast-light);
    text-decoration: underline wavy var(--accent-contrast-light);
}
/* Rss feed */
#HCB_comment_box a:last-child {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: 'Source Code Pro', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
}

#commentcredit {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: 'Source Code Pro', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
}
</style>